              "html": "<div style=\"background:#08122A;padding:160px 0 80px;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(196,154,42,0.15);position:relative;overflow:hidden;\"><div style=\"position:absolute;inset:0;background-image:linear-gradient(rgba(196,154,42,0.06) 1px,transparent 1px),linear-gradient(90deg,rgba(196,154,42,0.06) 1px,transparent 1px);background-size:60px 60px;pointer-events:none;\"></div><div style=\"max-width:1220px;margin:0 auto;padding:0 2.5rem;position:relative;z-index:1;\"><div style=\"font-family:DM Mono;font-size:10px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.3);letter-spacing:0.12em;text-transform:uppercase;margin-bottom:2rem;\"><a href=\"/\" style=\"color:rgba(255,255,255,0.3);text-decoration:none;\">Home</a> <span style=\"opacity:.4;\">/</span> <span style=\"color:#C49A2A;\">Partners &amp; Investors</span></div><div style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px;margin-bottom:1.5rem;\"><div style=\"width:40px;height:1px;background:#C49A2A;flex-shrink:0;\"></div><span style=\"font-family:DM Mono;font-size:10px;letter-spacing:0.2em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#C49A2A;\">Collaborate With Us</span></div><h1 style=\"font-family:Cormorant Garamond;font-size:clamp(2.8rem,5vw,5rem);font-weight:300;line-height:1.04;color:#FFFFFF;margin:0 0 0.4rem;\">Partner with</h1><h2 style=\"font-family:Cormorant Garamond;font-size:clamp(2.8rem,5vw,5rem);font-weight:700;line-height:1.04;color:#FFFFFF;margin:0 0 1.8rem;\"><em style=\"font-style:italic;color:#E2BF68;\">BMIIL</em></h2><p style=\"font-size:1rem;line-height:1.75;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.55);max-width:640px;margin:0 0 2.5rem;\">At BMIIL, we believe innovation thrives through collaboration. Your support \u2014 as an <strong style=\"color:#FFFFFF;\">investor, CSR partner, or mentor</strong> \u2014 helps transform visionary ideas into solutions that improve lives. Join us in powering India's medtech revolution.</p><div style=\"background:rgba(196,154,42,0.1);border:1px solid rgba(196,154,42,0.25);border-radius:4px;padding:1rem 1.5rem;display:inline-block;\"><p style=\"font-size:13px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.7);margin:0;\">\ud83c\udfdb\ufe0f BMIIL is a <strong style=\"color:#FFFFFF;\">Section 8 Company</strong> registered under the Companies Act 2013. All contributions &amp; investments are eligible for <strong style=\"color:#C49A2A;\">tax exemptions under Section 80G</strong> of the Income Tax Act.</p></div></div></div>"
