            "id": "u9nk3vj",
            "elType": "widget",
            "widgetType": "html",
            "settings": {
              "html": "<div style=\"background:#F7F3EC;padding:7rem 0;\"><div style=\"max-width:1220px;margin:0 auto;padding:0 2.5rem;\"><p style=\"display:inline-block;font-family:DM Mono;font-size:10px;letter-spacing:0.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#C49A2A;border:1px solid rgba(196,154,42,0.25);padding:4px 12px;border-radius:2px;background:rgba(196,154,42,0.08);margin:0 0 1.2rem;\">Ways to Collaborate</p><h2 style=\"font-family:Cormorant Garamond;font-size:clamp(2rem,4vw,3rem);font-weight:300;color:#08122A;margin:0 0 0.8rem;line-height:1.15;\">Together, let's ignite change in <strong style=\"font-weight:700;\">Healthcare.</strong></h2><p style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:1.8;color:#4A5C78;max-width:640px;margin:0 0 3rem;\">Whether you invest capital, expertise, or networks \u2014 every form of partnership accelerates the mission.</p><div style=\"display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:1.5rem;margin-bottom:5rem;\"><div style=\"background:#FFFFFF;border:1px solid #EDE8DE;border-radius:4px;padding:2rem;position:relative;overflow:hidden;\"><div style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;right:0;height:3px;background:#C49A2A;\"></div><div style=\"font-size:2rem;margin-bottom:0.8rem;\">\ud83d\udcb0</div><h3 style=\"font-family:Cormorant Garamond;font-size:1.3rem;font-weight:700;color:#08122A;margin:0 0 0.6rem;\">Investor</h3><p style=\"font-size:13px;line-height:1.65;color:#7A8BA8;margin:0 0 1.2rem;\">Deploy capital into India's fastest-growing medtech opportunity \u2014 Tier-2 India.</p><ul style=\"list-style:none;padding:0;margin:0;\"><li style=\"font-size:13px;color:#4A5C78;padding:0.4rem 0;border-bottom:1px solid #EDE8DE;display:flex;gap:8px;align-items:flex-start;\"><span style=\"color:#C49A2A;flex-shrink:0;\">\u2713</span>Equity & debt investment in portfolio startups</li><li style=\"font-size:13px;color:#4A5C78;padding:0.4rem 0;border-bottom:1px solid #EDE8DE;display:flex;gap:8px;align-items:flex-start;\"><span style=\"color:#C49A2A;flex-shrink:0;\">\u2713</span>Access to curated deal flow & due diligence</li><li style=\"font-size:13px;color:#4A5C78;padding:0.4rem 0;border-bottom:1px solid #EDE8DE;display:flex;gap:8px;align-items:flex-start;\"><span style=\"color:#C49A2A;flex-shrink:0;\">\u2713</span>Investor visibility at Demo Days & Pitch Events</li><li style=\"font-size:13px;color:#4A5C78;padding:0.4rem 0;border-bottom:1px solid #EDE8DE;display:flex;gap:8px;align-items:flex-start;\"><span style=\"color:#C49A2A;flex-shrink:0;\">\u2713</span>Co-investment opportunities with other funds</li></ul></div><div style=\"background:#FFFFFF;border:1px solid #EDE8DE;border-radius:4px;padding:2rem;position:relative;overflow:hidden;\"><div style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;right:0;height:3px;background:#C49A2A;\"></div><div style=\"font-size:2rem;margin-bottom:0.8rem;\">\ud83e\udd1d</div><h3 style=\"font-family:Cormorant Garamond;font-size:1.3rem;font-weight:700;color:#08122A;margin:0 0 0.6rem;\">Corporate Partner / CSR</h3><p style=\"font-size:13px;line-height:1.65;color:#7A8BA8;margin:0 0 1.2rem;\">Align your CSR mandate with tangible healthcare innovation impact.</p><ul style=\"list-style:none;padding:0;margin:0;\"><li style=\"font-size:13px;color:#4A5C78;padding:0.4rem 0;border-bottom:1px solid #EDE8DE;display:flex;gap:8px;align-items:flex-start;\"><span style=\"color:#C49A2A;flex-shrink:0;\">\u2713</span>Section 80G tax exemptions on contributions</li><li style=\"font-size:13px;color:#4A5C78;padding:0.4rem 0;border-bottom:1px solid #EDE8DE;display:flex;gap:8px;align-items:flex-start;\"><span style=\"color:#C49A2A;flex-shrink:0;\">\u2713</span>Brand visibility across BMIIL platforms & events</li><li style=\"font-size:13px;color:#4A5C78;padding:0.4rem 0;border-bottom:1px solid #EDE8DE;display:flex;gap:8px;align-items:flex-start;\"><span style=\"color:#C49A2A;flex-shrink:0;\">\u2713</span>Structured CSR reporting & impact documentation</li><li style=\"font-size:13px;color:#4A5C78;padding:0.4rem 0;border-bottom:1px solid #EDE8DE;display:flex;gap:8px;align-items:flex-start;\"><span style=\"color:#C49A2A;flex-shrink:0;\">\u2713</span>Employee engagement through mentorship programs</li></ul></div><div style=\"background:#FFFFFF;border:1px solid #EDE8DE;border-radius:4px;padding:2rem;position:relative;overflow:hidden;\"><div style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;right:0;height:3px;background:#C49A2A;\"></div><div style=\"font-size:2rem;margin-bottom:0.8rem;\">\ud83e\udde0</div><h3 style=\"font-family:Cormorant Garamond;font-size:1.3rem;font-weight:700;color:#08122A;margin:0 0 0.6rem;\">Mentor / Expert</h3><p style=\"font-size:13px;line-height:1.65;color:#7A8BA8;margin:0 0 1.2rem;\">Share your domain expertise to help early-stage founders succeed.</p><ul style=\"list-style:none;padding:0;margin:0;\"><li style=\"font-size:13px;color:#4A5C78;padding:0.4rem 0;border-bottom:1px solid #EDE8DE;display:flex;gap:8px;align-items:flex-start;\"><span style=\"color:#C49A2A;flex-shrink:0;\">\u2713</span>1:1 mentorship with vetted medtech startups</li><li style=\"font-size:13px;color:#4A5C78;padding:0.4rem 0;border-bottom:1px solid #EDE8DE;display:flex;gap:8px;align-items:flex-start;\"><span style=\"color:#C49A2A;flex-shrink:0;\">\u2713</span>Flexible time commitment \u2014 monthly or quarterly</li><li style=\"font-size:13px;color:#4A5C78;padding:0.4rem 0;border-bottom:1px solid #EDE8DE;display:flex;gap:8px;align-items:flex-start;\"><span style=\"color:#C49A2A;flex-shrink:0;\">\u2713</span>Advisory board positions available</li><li style=\"font-size:13px;color:#4A5C78;padding:0.4rem 0;border-bottom:1px solid #EDE8DE;display:flex;gap:8px;align-items:flex-start;\"><span style=\"color:#C49A2A;flex-shrink:0;\">\u2713</span>Access to BMIIL's research & clinical networks</li></ul></div><div style=\"background:#FFFFFF;border:1px solid #EDE8DE;border-radius:4px;padding:2rem;position:relative;overflow:hidden;\"><div style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;right:0;height:3px;background:#C49A2A;\"></div><div style=\"font-size:2rem;margin-bottom:0.8rem;\">\ud83d\udd2c</div><h3 style=\"font-family:Cormorant Garamond;font-size:1.3rem;font-weight:700;color:#08122A;margin:0 0 0.6rem;\">Research Partner</h3><p style=\"font-size:13px;line-height:1.65;color:#7A8BA8;margin:0 0 1.2rem;\">Collaborate on clinical validation, IP development, and publications.</p><ul style=\"list-style:none;padding:0;margin:0;\"><li style=\"font-size:13px;color:#4A5C78;padding:0.4rem 0;border-bottom:1px solid #EDE8DE;display:flex;gap:8px;align-items:flex-start;\"><span style=\"color:#C49A2A;flex-shrink:0;\">\u2713</span>Joint research with BIU faculty & departments</li><li style=\"font-size:13px;color:#4A5C78;padding:0.4rem 0;border-bottom:1px solid #EDE8DE;display:flex;gap:8px;align-items:flex-start;\"><span style=\"color:#C49A2A;flex-shrink:0;\">\u2713</span>Access to hospital data & patient cohorts</li><li style=\"font-size:13px;color:#4A5C78;padding:0.4rem 0;border-bottom:1px solid #EDE8DE;display:flex;gap:8px;align-items:flex-start;\"><span style=\"color:#C49A2A;flex-shrink:0;\">\u2713</span>Co-authorship on publications & grant proposals</li><li style=\"font-size:13px;color:#4A5C78;padding:0.4rem 0;border-bottom:1px solid #EDE8DE;display:flex;gap:8px;align-items:flex-start;\"><span style=\"color:#C49A2A;flex-shrink:0;\">\u2713</span>IP co-ownership structures available</li></ul></div><div style=\"background:#FFFFFF;border:1px solid #EDE8DE;border-radius:4px;padding:2rem;position:relative;overflow:hidden;\"><div style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;right:0;height:3px;background:#C49A2A;\"></div><div style=\"font-size:2rem;margin-bottom:0.8rem;\">\ud83c\udfe5</div><h3 style=\"font-family:Cormorant Garamond;font-size:1.3rem;font-weight:700;color:#08122A;margin:0 0 0.6rem;\">Hospital / Clinical Partner</h3><p style=\"font-size:13px;line-height:1.65;color:#7A8BA8;margin:0 0 1.2rem;\">Provide clinical environments for startup validation and piloting.</p><ul style=\"list-style:none;padding:0;margin:0;\"><li style=\"font-size:13px;color:#4A5C78;padding:0.4rem 0;border-bottom:1px solid #EDE8DE;display:flex;gap:8px;align-items:flex-start;\"><span style=\"color:#C49A2A;flex-shrink:0;\">\u2713</span>Pilot programs within your clinical setting</li><li style=\"font-size:13px;color:#4A5C78;padding:0.4rem 0;border-bottom:1px solid #EDE8DE;display:flex;gap:8px;align-items:flex-start;\"><span style=\"color:#C49A2A;flex-shrink:0;\">\u2713</span>First access to validated medtech solutions</li><li style=\"font-size:13px;color:#4A5C78;padding:0.4rem 0;border-bottom:1px solid #EDE8DE;display:flex;gap:8px;align-items:flex-start;\"><span style=\"color:#C49A2A;flex-shrink:0;\">\u2713</span>Revenue sharing on successful deployments</li><li style=\"font-size:13px;color:#4A5C78;padding:0.4rem 0;border-bottom:1px solid #EDE8DE;display:flex;gap:8px;align-items:flex-start;\"><span style=\"color:#C49A2A;flex-shrink:0;\">\u2713</span>Visibility as an innovation partner</li></ul></div><div style=\"background:#FFFFFF;border:1px solid #EDE8DE;border-radius:4px;padding:2rem;position:relative;overflow:hidden;\"><div style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;right:0;height:3px;background:#C49A2A;\"></div><div style=\"font-size:2rem;margin-bottom:0.8rem;\">\ud83c\udf0d</div><h3 style=\"font-family:Cormorant Garamond;font-size:1.3rem;font-weight:700;color:#08122A;margin:0 0 0.6rem;\">International Partner</h3><p style=\"font-size:13px;line-height:1.65;color:#7A8BA8;margin:0 0 1.2rem;\">Connect BMIIL startups to global markets, networks, and opportunities.</p><ul style=\"list-style:none;padding:0;margin:0;\"><li style=\"font-size:13px;color:#4A5C78;padding:0.4rem 0;border-bottom:1px solid #EDE8DE;display:flex;gap:8px;align-items:flex-start;\"><span style=\"color:#C49A2A;flex-shrink:0;\">\u2713</span>MOU-based partnership with BMIIL</li><li style=\"font-size:13px;color:#4A5C78;padding:0.4rem 0;border-bottom:1px solid #EDE8DE;display:flex;gap:8px;align-items:flex-start;\"><span style=\"color:#C49A2A;flex-shrink:0;\">\u2713</span>Cross-border startup exchange programs</li><li style=\"font-size:13px;color:#4A5C78;padding:0.4rem 0;border-bottom:1px solid #EDE8DE;display:flex;gap:8px;align-items:flex-start;\"><span style=\"color:#C49A2A;flex-shrink:0;\">\u2713</span>Joint demo days and investor introductions</li><li style=\"font-size:13px;color:#4A5C78;padding:0.4rem 0;border-bottom:1px solid #EDE8DE;display:flex;gap:8px;align-items:flex-start;\"><span style=\"color:#C49A2A;flex-shrink:0;\">\u2713</span>Global market access for portfolio companies</li></ul></div></div><div style=\"background:#08122A;border-radius:4px;padding:3rem 3.5rem;\"><div style=\"display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:4rem;align-items:center;\"><div><h3 style=\"font-family:Cormorant Garamond;font-size:2rem;font-weight:300;color:#FFFFFF;margin:0 0 1.5rem;\">Why partner with BMIIL?</h3><div style=\"display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:1rem;\"><div style=\"display:flex;gap:1rem;align-items:flex-start;\"><div style=\"width:32px;height:32px;border-radius:50%;background:rgba(196,154,42,0.15);border:1px solid rgba(196,154,42,0.3);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;flex-shrink:0;font-size:0.9rem;\">\ud83c\udfaf</div><div><div style=\"font-weight:600;color:#FFFFFF;font-size:14px;margin-bottom:2px;\">First Mover Advantage</div><div style=\"font-size:13px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.5);line-height:1.5;\">Tier-2 India medtech is underserved \u2014 be among the first institutional backers.</div></div></div><div style=\"display:flex;gap:1rem;align-items:flex-start;\"><div style=\"width:32px;height:32px;border-radius:50%;background:rgba(196,154,42,0.15);border:1px solid rgba(196,154,42,0.3);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;flex-shrink:0;font-size:0.9rem;\">\ud83c\udfe5</div><div><div style=\"font-weight:600;color:#FFFFFF;font-size:14px;margin-bottom:2px;\">Clinical Validation Pipeline</div><div style=\"font-size:13px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.5);line-height:1.5;\">Direct access to BIU's 1200+ bed hospital for real-world validation.</div></div></div><div style=\"display:flex;gap:1rem;align-items:flex-start;\"><div style=\"width:32px;height:32px;border-radius:50%;background:rgba(196,154,42,0.15);border:1px solid rgba(196,154,42,0.3);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;flex-shrink:0;font-size:0.9rem;\">\ud83d\udcca</div><div><div style=\"font-weight:600;color:#FFFFFF;font-size:14px;margin-bottom:2px;\">Transparent Impact Reporting</div><div style=\"font-size:13px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.5);line-height:1.5;\">Quarterly updates, milestone tracking, and CSR documentation.</div></div></div><div style=\"display:flex;gap:1rem;align-items:flex-start;\"><div style=\"width:32px;height:32px;border-radius:50%;background:rgba(196,154,42,0.15);border:1px solid rgba(196,154,42,0.3);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;flex-shrink:0;font-size:0.9rem;\">\ud83d\udd12</div><div><div style=\"font-weight:600;color:#FFFFFF;font-size:14px;margin-bottom:2px;\">Section 80G Tax Benefits</div><div style=\"font-size:13px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.5);line-height:1.5;\">All contributions eligible for income tax deductions under Section 80G.</div></div></div></div></div><div style=\"display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:1rem;\"><div style=\"background:rgba(255,255,255,0.05);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);border-radius:4px;padding:1.2rem 1.5rem;\"><div style=\"font-family:DM Mono;font-size:10px;letter-spacing:0.15em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#C49A2A;margin-bottom:0.3rem;\">Hospital Access</div><div style=\"font-family:Cormorant Garamond;font-size:1.8rem;font-weight:700;color:#FFFFFF;\">1,200+</div><div style=\"font-size:12px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.4);margin-top:2px;\">Bed teaching hospital for clinical validation</div></div><div style=\"background:rgba(255,255,255,0.05);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);border-radius:4px;padding:1.2rem 1.5rem;\"><div style=\"font-family:DM Mono;font-size:10px;letter-spacing:0.15em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#C49A2A;margin-bottom:0.3rem;\">Research Faculty</div><div style=\"font-family:Cormorant Garamond;font-size:1.8rem;font-weight:700;color:#FFFFFF;\">200+</div><div style=\"font-size:12px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.4);margin-top:2px;\">Multidisciplinary experts across BIU colleges</div></div><div style=\"background:rgba(255,255,255,0.05);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);border-radius:4px;padding:1.2rem 1.5rem;\"><div style=\"font-family:DM Mono;font-size:10px;letter-spacing:0.15em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#C49A2A;margin-bottom:0.3rem;\">Program Tracks</div><div style=\"font-family:Cormorant Garamond;font-size:1.8rem;font-weight:700;color:#FFFFFF;\">3</div><div style=\"font-size:12px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.4);margin-top:2px;\">Medtech \u00b7 Accelerator \u00b7 Ayush Incubation</div></div><div style=\"background:rgba(255,255,255,0.05);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);border-radius:4px;padding:1.2rem 1.5rem;\"><div style=\"font-family:DM Mono;font-size:10px;letter-spacing:0.15em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#C49A2A;margin-bottom:0.3rem;\">Target Cohort</div><div style=\"font-family:Cormorant Garamond;font-size:1.8rem;font-weight:700;color:#FFFFFF;\">12</div><div style=\"font-size:12px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.4);margin-top:2px;\">Startups in inaugural batch \u2014 limited seats</div></div></div></div></div></div></div>"
